00:06:19.512 --> 00:06:21.264 line:80%
Are you throwing a tantrum?

00:06:22.974 --> 00:06:24.392 line:80%
Premarital pregnancy…

00:06:28.688 --> 00:06:29.981 line:80%
You can rest assured

00:06:30.607 --> 00:06:32.317 line:80%
that no such tantrum will be thrown.

00:06:43.703 --> 00:06:46.206 line:80%
Your Royal Highness,
Public Affairs has reached out.

00:06:46.915 --> 00:06:48.041 line:80%
What are you doing here?

00:06:48.625 --> 00:06:50.668 line:80%
-Pardon?
-You should be guarding Anhwadang Hall.

00:06:51.920 --> 00:06:53.254 line:80%
To keep an eye on Seong Huiju.

00:06:54.172 --> 00:06:55.298 line:80%
But… [sighs]

00:06:55.381 --> 00:06:56.466 line:80%
My apologies.

00:07:06.893 --> 00:07:08.102 line:80%
Seong Huiju.

00:07:08.186 --> 00:07:09.562 line:80%
Oh. You're here.

00:07:09.646 --> 00:07:11.064 line:80%
Uncle.

00:07:11.606 --> 00:07:12.732 line:80%
