00:07:35.129 --> 00:07:37.257 line:80%
[King] I was having trouble sleeping.
[sucks teeth]

00:07:42.679 --> 00:07:43.680 line:80%
[exhales deeply]

00:07:43.763 --> 00:07:45.223 line:80%
So I came by.

00:07:45.723 --> 00:07:47.225 line:80%
What does having trouble sleeping

00:07:48.935 --> 00:07:50.228 line:80%
