would help me fall asleep.

00:08:05.910 --> 00:08:07.203 line:80%
Come in, Court Lady Jung.

00:08:16.004 --> 00:08:17.005 line:80%
Your Majesty.

00:08:18.715 --> 00:08:20.717 line:80%
Shall I escort you
to Queen Mother's quarters?

00:08:30.643 --> 00:08:32.812 line:80%
You couldn't just let him
finish it in peace?

00:08:33.813 --> 00:08:34.897 line:80%
[sighs]

00:08:37.191 --> 00:08:38.860 line:80%
I mean, come on.

00:08:39.402 --> 00:08:42.113 line:80%
A bowl of <i>ramyeon</i>
wouldn't have taken that long to finish.

00:08:45.992 --> 00:08:47.493 line:80%
And if he suffers indigestion?

00:08:48.328 --> 00:08:49.662 line:80%
You would be wholly to blame.

00:08:50.496 --> 00:08:52.415 line:80%
-And if Queen Mother is angered?
-[scoffs]

00:08:52.999 --> 00:08:55.043 line:80%
All that over a measly bowl of <i>ramyeon</i>?

00:08:55.126 --> 00:08:56.169 line:80%
The Queen Mother…

00:08:58.463 --> 00:08:59.464 line:80%
