00:09:11.017 --> 00:09:13.269 line:80%
But you know, it still doesn't feel great.

00:09:13.353 --> 00:09:14.979 line:80%
Like I'm being bullied by my in-laws.

00:09:15.063 --> 00:09:16.898 line:80%
Wait! Hold on a second.

00:09:17.732 --> 00:09:19.817 line:80%
What will you do
if my in-laws really bully me?

00:09:20.860 --> 00:09:23.654 line:80%
I mean, just look at
how things are unfolding already.

00:09:23.738 --> 00:09:26.783 line:80%
Let's say the Queen Mother
and I got into a fight.

00:09:26.866 --> 00:09:28.868 line:80%
Would you take my side?

00:09:29.827 --> 00:09:30.828 line:80%
