00:09:39.879 --> 00:09:41.214 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:09:41.881 --> 00:09:42.965 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:09:44.550 --> 00:09:45.676 line:80%
I will take your side.

00:09:54.185 --> 00:09:55.186 line:80%
I must appear

00:09:56.396 --> 00:09:57.688 line:80%
