00:10:34.434 --> 00:10:36.686 line:80%
Get her a change of clothes as well.

00:10:37.854 --> 00:10:38.855 line:80%
Clothes?

00:10:39.480 --> 00:10:40.606 line:80%
-Huh?
-[chuckles]

00:10:41.274 --> 00:10:44.277 line:80%
Can I get something that's 100% cotton?

00:10:46.821 --> 00:10:48.948 line:80%
My skin's a little sensitive.

00:10:50.199 --> 00:10:51.367 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:10:55.788 --> 00:10:57.415 line:80%
[exhales deeply]

00:11:02.879 --> 00:11:04.672 line:80%
[I-AN]
Will you not even consider the sofa?

00:11:05.173 --> 00:11:07.884 line:80%
No. This is perfectly fine.

00:11:13.139 --> 00:11:14.765 line:80%
The sofa would be perfectly fine too.

00:11:14.849 --> 00:11:18.311 line:80%
Then you should go. That'd be perfect.

00:11:25.359 --> 00:11:26.861 line:80%
[♪ whimsical music playing]

00:11:30.573 --> 00:11:31.657 line:80%
[grunts]

00:11:32.700 --> 00:11:34.243 line:80%
-[grunts]
-[grunts]

00:11:36.370 --> 00:11:37.413 line:80%
[sighs]

00:11:39.916 --> 00:11:40.917 line:80%
[grunts]

00:11:47.215 --> 00:11:48.216 line:80%
[grunts]

00:11:51.469 --> 00:11:52.970 line:80%
-[grunts]
-[strains]

00:11:56.098 --> 00:11:57.350 line:80%
[screams]

00:11:57.850 --> 00:11:58.851 line:80%
