00:12:11.280 --> 00:12:13.032 line:80%
-Oh, my.
-[Huiju] Your Royal Highness.

00:12:14.283 --> 00:12:15.493 line:80%
-Your Royal Highness!
-[shudders]

00:12:15.576 --> 00:12:16.827 line:80%
-[I-AN] Stay still!
-[exclaims]

00:12:20.373 --> 00:12:21.832 line:80%
[Hyeon] Your Royal Highness.

00:12:24.252 --> 00:12:26.337 line:80%
-[shouts] Your Royal Highness!
-What? Stay still…

00:12:28.256 --> 00:12:29.549 line:80%
My goodness.

00:12:29.632 --> 00:12:31.634 line:80%
[Hyeon]
Do you know what time it is right now?

00:12:32.343 --> 00:12:34.512 line:80%
It's unlike you to sleep in like this.

00:12:35.513 --> 00:12:36.514 line:80%
[gasps]

00:12:39.892 --> 00:12:42.186 line:80%
[smacks lips]
Ms. Seong is already on her way to work.

00:12:42.270 --> 00:12:43.896 line:80%
With a pep in her step, at that.

00:12:45.856 --> 00:12:46.899 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:12:59.662 --> 00:13:01.122 line:80%
[♪ upbeat music playing]

00:13:04.041 --> 00:13:05.626 line:80%
-[sighs]
-You didn't change?

00:13:06.210 --> 00:13:07.378 line:80%
No. Something wrong?

00:13:14.802 --> 00:13:17.346 line:80%
Are you trying to show off
that you spent the night out?

00:13:17.430 --> 00:13:18.889 line:80%
