00:15:37.278 --> 00:15:40.281 line:80%
Ah. Do not worry, Your Majesty.

00:15:40.781 --> 00:15:44.910 line:80%
You will always have
your grandfather by your side.

00:15:46.370 --> 00:15:47.747 line:80%
[laughs]

00:15:47.830 --> 00:15:48.831 line:80%
Go on.

00:16:01.761 --> 00:16:03.596 line:80%
FAMILY APPRECIATION
MONTH EVENT REPORT

00:16:25.326 --> 00:16:27.286 line:80%
