00:16:28.537 --> 00:16:32.249 line:20%
"A royal child out of wedlock?
That's insane."

00:16:33.083 --> 00:16:35.336 line:80%
That's right. It's totally insane.

00:16:36.670 --> 00:16:39.423 line:20%
