00:17:11.539 --> 00:17:13.499 line:80%
[stutters] The PR team? Why?

00:17:13.582 --> 00:17:14.583 line:80%
Why else?

00:17:15.251 --> 00:17:18.254 line:80%
It's time to take back
the number-one spot in sales.

00:17:19.380 --> 00:17:21.340 line:80%
How can you even
think about that right now?

00:17:22.633 --> 00:17:24.009 line:80%
It's marriage, not retirement.

00:17:24.093 --> 00:17:25.135 line:80%
[knock on door]

00:17:28.472 --> 00:17:30.558 line:80%
Oh. Jeongwoo?

00:17:31.225 --> 00:17:32.226 line:80%
[Hyejeong] Hello, sir.

00:17:32.977 --> 00:17:35.187 line:80%
-[coworker] Isn't he so handsome?
-Super handsome!

00:17:35.271 --> 00:17:37.898 line:80%
This is my first time seeing
Prime Minister Min in person.

00:17:37.982 --> 00:17:40.109 line:80%
[squeals] He looks like a total celebrity.

00:17:40.192 --> 00:17:41.902 line:80%
Right. But what's he doing here?

00:17:41.986 --> 00:17:43.112 line:80%
Maybe because of the scandal?

00:17:43.195 --> 00:17:45.656 line:80%
-Oh! That must be--
-Why is no one working?

00:17:48.492 --> 00:17:50.953 line:80%
You're really going to marry him?

00:17:51.704 --> 00:17:53.330 line:80%
-Yeah.
-His Royal Highness?

00:17:53.414 --> 00:17:54.832 line:80%
Yeah.

00:17:54.915 --> 00:17:56.542 line:80%
I thought you two had just met.

00:17:57.167 --> 00:17:58.627 line:80%
Can't you just stick to dating?

00:17:58.711 --> 00:18:01.088 line:80%
But I want to be with him all the time.

00:18:01.922 --> 00:18:04.592 line:80%
-[chuckles] Huiju…
-I want to wake up next to him

00:18:05.217 --> 00:18:06.260 line:80%
every day.

00:18:08.804 --> 00:18:10.931 line:80%
I hear the royal family

00:18:11.015 --> 00:18:13.434 line:80%
wants to marry him off to someone else.

00:18:15.519 --> 00:18:18.856 line:80%
-[sighs]
-That's why I have to marry him right now.

00:18:19.440 --> 00:18:20.858 line:80%
While you're the Prime Minister.

00:18:26.071 --> 00:18:27.406 line:80%
I need you to get

00:18:28.824 --> 00:18:29.825 line:80%
my marriage approved.

00:18:39.209 --> 00:18:42.129 line:80%
We're planning to invite
the top 300 patrons in the country.

00:18:42.713 --> 00:18:44.965 line:80%
-[I-AN] What are the criteria?
-Your Royal Highness.

00:18:50.638 --> 00:18:51.639 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:18:59.521 --> 00:19:01.941 line:80%
The Queen Mother has taken to her sickbed.

00:19:02.024 --> 00:19:03.317 line:80%
All of a sudden?

00:19:03.400 --> 00:19:05.861 line:80%
Perhaps it's a ploy
to prevent an official statement.

00:19:05.945 --> 00:19:08.948 line:80%
The palace cannot speak of celebrations
while a royal elder lies ill.

00:19:12.701 --> 00:19:13.702 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:19:14.912 --> 00:19:16.038 line:80%
[phone buzzing]

00:19:16.121 --> 00:19:17.623 line:80%
JUNIOR ALUM

00:19:18.832 --> 00:19:20.000 line:80%
Understood. You may leave.

00:19:25.714 --> 00:19:27.132 line:80%
[Huiju] <i>Your Royal Highness!</i>

00:19:28.634 --> 00:19:30.260 line:80%
I hear you fine. Lower your voice.

00:19:31.095 --> 00:19:32.221 line:80%
<i>Did you read the article?</i>

00:19:34.098 --> 00:19:35.474 line:80%
Right before it was pulled.

00:19:36.266 --> 00:19:38.018 line:80%
It was taken down at lightning speed.

00:19:38.102 --> 00:19:39.895 line:80%
<i>The Queen Mother has been very busy.</i>

00:19:39.979 --> 00:19:41.981 line:80%
I guess even nobles can move quickly

00:19:42.064 --> 00:19:43.440 line:80%
when they want to.

00:19:44.483 --> 00:19:45.484 line:80%
[groans]

00:19:46.068 --> 00:19:47.236 line:80%
-[gasps]
-[students laughing]

00:19:47.778 --> 00:19:48.779 line:80%
[I-AN] <i>Seong Huiju?</i>

00:19:49.321 --> 00:19:50.322 line:80%
Oh?

00:19:51.532 --> 00:19:52.783 line:80%
You sly fox!

00:19:52.866 --> 00:19:54.827 line:80%
You dare try to seduce His Royal Highness!

00:19:55.869 --> 00:19:57.496 line:80%
-"Fox"?
-Yeah, you fox!

00:19:58.247 --> 00:20:01.083 line:80%
-Oh, my gosh!
-Stay away from His Royal Highness!

00:20:01.166 --> 00:20:03.711 line:80%
-Get lost!
-Hey, good job.

00:20:05.629 --> 00:20:06.714 line:80%
Seong Huiju?

00:20:06.797 --> 00:20:08.465 line:80%
Should we? Should we not?

00:20:09.133 --> 00:20:10.217 line:80%
Come here, you brats.

00:20:10.300 --> 00:20:13.095 line:80%
-We could throw them all.
-"Come here, you brats!"

00:20:15.222 --> 00:20:16.765 line:80%
Get over here now!

00:20:32.531 --> 00:20:33.532 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:20:36.160 --> 00:20:37.369 line:80%
What is all that?

00:20:37.453 --> 00:20:39.329 line:80%
Is it not obvious? These are your duties.

00:20:39.413 --> 00:20:40.956 line:80%
-All of it?
-All of it.

00:20:43.000 --> 00:20:45.502 line:80%
-That cannot be true.
-It most certainly is.

00:20:45.586 --> 00:20:49.173 line:80%
These are the duties you are
to carry out on His Majesty's behalf.

00:20:49.840 --> 00:20:53.135 line:80%
These are the Queen Mother's… Goodness.
This stack is quite heavy.

00:20:53.218 --> 00:20:56.346 line:80%
These are the Queen Mother's duties
you are to carry out

00:20:57.056 --> 00:20:58.348 line:80%
in her absence.

00:20:58.432 --> 00:21:01.143 line:80%
And these are your duties
that accumulated while you were away.

00:21:01.810 --> 00:21:03.520 line:80%
-You got this.
-Get out.

00:21:03.604 --> 00:21:04.897 line:80%
Yes, sir.

00:21:05.481 --> 00:21:07.524 line:80%
Let's go. Off we go.

00:21:11.653 --> 00:21:14.907 line:80%
You little brats should be in school
with your noses in books.

00:21:14.990 --> 00:21:16.492 line:80%
Eyes down!

00:21:17.701 --> 00:21:20.287 line:80%
Does Prince I-AN put food on your table?

00:21:20.370 --> 00:21:22.498 line:80%
He may not feed us, but he gives us money.

00:21:22.581 --> 00:21:25.000 line:80%
-Right.
-We're royal scholarship students.

00:21:25.793 --> 00:21:27.753 line:80%
That money was for your studies.

00:21:27.836 --> 00:21:30.964 line:80%
Do you think he wanted you to spend
that money buying eggs to throw?

00:21:31.632 --> 00:21:32.758 line:80%
And you, Hyerin.

00:21:33.300 --> 00:21:35.511 line:80%
Why did you assume I seduced him?

00:21:35.594 --> 00:21:36.595 line:80%
Isn't it obvious?

00:21:36.678 --> 00:21:37.888 line:80%
Why, you little…

00:21:37.971 --> 00:21:40.724 line:80%
So young and already full of prejudice.

00:21:40.808 --> 00:21:42.684 line:80%
If I had it my way,

00:21:43.435 --> 00:21:47.272 line:80%
I'd give you hell and take legal action
for pulling something like this…

00:21:48.816 --> 00:21:49.983 line:80%
Come here.

00:21:51.110 --> 00:21:52.361 line:80%
But right now,

00:21:52.945 --> 00:21:55.364 line:80%
your big sis here has
a major undertaking ahead of her.

00:21:56.031 --> 00:21:58.158 line:80%
So I'll let it slide just this once.

00:21:58.867 --> 00:21:59.868 line:80%
Got it?

00:22:01.370 --> 00:22:03.205 line:80%
-Answer me!
-Yes, ma'am!

00:22:06.792 --> 00:22:08.168 line:80%
Off you go.

00:22:08.252 --> 00:22:09.628 line:80%
<i>Almighty God.</i>

00:22:10.796 --> 00:22:12.965 line:80%
Please have mercy on us,

00:22:13.966 --> 00:22:15.592 line:80%
forgive us our sins,

00:22:16.677 --> 00:22:20.347 line:80%
and bring us to everlasting life.

00:22:21.849 --> 00:22:22.850 line:80%
Amen.

00:22:26.645 --> 00:22:27.896 line:80%
Amen.

00:22:30.107 --> 00:22:32.192 line:80%
You said you couldn't come for a while.

00:22:33.485 --> 00:22:36.613 line:80%
I heard my friend is getting married,
so I came to pray.

00:22:37.948 --> 00:22:41.243 line:80%
That friend is very lucky to have you
praying for her happiness.

00:22:41.827 --> 00:22:42.828 line:80%
I'm not so sure.

00:22:43.787 --> 00:22:45.122 line:80%
I prayed for something sinful.

00:22:46.623 --> 00:22:47.791 line:80%
[stutters] Something sinful?

00:22:49.710 --> 00:22:50.919 line:80%
I do not feel inclined

00:22:51.837 --> 00:22:53.172 line:80%
to congratulate her.

00:22:56.508 --> 00:22:58.468 line:80%
[♪ soft music playing]

00:22:59.970 --> 00:23:01.054 line:80%
[object clatters]

00:23:06.059 --> 00:23:08.729 line:80%
[Jeongwoo]
<i>But I don't want to stop her either.</i>

00:23:14.902 --> 00:23:16.445 line:80%
<i>Even if I don't think it's right…</i>

00:23:17.362 --> 00:23:18.780 line:80%
Damn it.

00:23:18.864 --> 00:23:21.033 line:80%
Where did that punk hide it?

00:23:21.617 --> 00:23:23.327 line:80%
[Jeongwoo] <i>If that's what she wants…</i>

00:23:25.245 --> 00:23:27.080 line:80%
-Ma'am.
-[teacher] Hey, Jeongwoo.

00:23:27.164 --> 00:23:28.540 line:80%
Are you running an errand?

00:23:28.624 --> 00:23:31.126 line:80%
[chuckles] Yes.

00:23:31.210 --> 00:23:33.128 line:80%
Principal Kim was looking for you earlier.

00:23:33.212 --> 00:23:34.463 line:80%
Did you see him?

00:23:35.464 --> 00:23:36.673 line:80%
[Jeongwoo] <i>…I have to let her.</i>

00:23:37.382 --> 00:23:38.592 line:80%
Found it.

00:23:41.303 --> 00:23:42.304 line:80%
Got it.

00:23:45.015 --> 00:23:46.892 line:80%
[door opens, closes]

00:23:56.235 --> 00:23:57.277 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:24:09.331 --> 00:24:12.542 line:80%
I mean, how did those brats
even get past security?

00:24:13.460 --> 00:24:16.255 line:80%
You have to hand it
to the high schoolers in this country.

00:24:25.722 --> 00:24:26.723 line:80%
Father?

00:24:38.902 --> 00:24:41.947 line:80%
[stammers] Can I get you anything?

00:24:44.992 --> 00:24:46.159 line:80%
Don't bother. Sit.

00:24:55.043 --> 00:24:56.461 line:80%
About that scandal…

00:24:56.545 --> 00:24:58.213 line:80%
No need to explain.

00:24:59.673 --> 00:25:03.510 line:80%
-You're not curious?
-There's nothing to be curious about.

00:25:03.593 --> 00:25:04.594 line:80%
I'm sure

00:25:05.095 --> 00:25:07.389 line:80%
it's just a cheap stunt
you pulled for attention.

00:25:10.183 --> 00:25:11.351 line:80%
Then why are you here?

00:25:15.939 --> 00:25:16.940 line:80%
It's nearly…

00:25:18.442 --> 00:25:19.985 line:80%
Taeju's mother's death anniversary.

00:25:21.820 --> 00:25:23.739 line:80%
I was wondering if you even remembered.

00:25:27.451 --> 00:25:28.452 line:80%
Ma'am.

00:25:32.622 --> 00:25:34.833 line:80%
She's been standing
outside the house for hours,

00:25:35.459 --> 00:25:37.294 line:80%
but she refuses to talk.

00:25:37.878 --> 00:25:40.881 line:80%
Then you should've reported her
to the police, not brought her inside.

00:25:41.506 --> 00:25:42.632 line:80%
Send her away.

00:25:42.716 --> 00:25:45.635 line:80%
How can we just send away a child
in the middle of the night?

00:25:47.888 --> 00:25:50.474 line:80%
Little one, are you lost?

00:25:53.018 --> 00:25:54.186 line:80%
What's your name?

00:25:58.398 --> 00:25:59.816 line:80%
You don't want to say?

00:26:03.153 --> 00:26:04.488 line:80%
I am

00:26:05.072 --> 00:26:06.740 line:80%
Lee Jooyeon's daughter.

00:26:12.371 --> 00:26:13.538 line:80%
You're my dad…

00:26:14.456 --> 00:26:15.457 line:80%
aren't you?

00:26:24.341 --> 00:26:25.634 line:80%
[sobs]

00:26:28.720 --> 00:26:30.514 line:80%
-Honey! Honey!
-Mom!

00:26:30.597 --> 00:26:32.849 line:80%
-Ma'am! Wake up, ma'am!
-Honey!

00:26:32.933 --> 00:26:35.227 line:80%
-Honey!
-Ma'am!

00:26:35.769 --> 00:26:37.938 line:80%
-Ma'am! Oh, dear goodness!
-Mom, wake up!

00:26:38.021 --> 00:26:40.524 line:80%
[Hyeonguk]
<i>Since the day your mother abandoned you…</i>

00:26:40.607 --> 00:26:41.900 line:80%
-[muffled] Ma'am.
-Mommy!

00:26:41.983 --> 00:26:43.777 line:80%
[Hyeonguk] <i>…our lives fell into despair.</i>

00:26:51.785 --> 00:26:53.245 line:80%
CERTIFICATE OF AWARD

00:26:53.328 --> 00:26:55.622 line:80%
Buy me a bike too.

00:26:55.705 --> 00:26:58.375 line:80%
The same one as Taeju.

00:27:01.002 --> 00:27:03.338 line:80%
[Hyeonguk] <i>You dared to be greedy…</i>

00:27:03.922 --> 00:27:05.132 line:80%
REPORT CARD

00:27:06.133 --> 00:27:07.801 line:80%
I want a building too.

00:27:07.884 --> 00:27:09.719 line:80%
One that's taller than Taeju's.

00:27:09.803 --> 00:27:11.054 line:80%
[Hyeonguk] <i>So greedy…</i>

00:27:12.055 --> 00:27:13.056 line:80%
STOCK PRICE ANALYSIS

00:27:13.140 --> 00:27:14.808 line:80%
Amend your will, Father.

00:27:15.475 --> 00:27:16.726 line:80%
In my favor.

00:27:16.810 --> 00:27:18.437 line:80%
[Hyeonguk] <i>Your greed was relentless!</i>

00:27:25.110 --> 00:27:26.862 line:80%
Keep your hands off the company.

00:27:26.945 --> 00:27:27.988 line:80%
And if I don't?

00:27:28.071 --> 00:27:29.698 line:80%
I'll have no choice but to act.

00:27:29.781 --> 00:27:30.782 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:27:31.616 --> 00:27:33.785 line:80%
-What? Are you going to disown me?
-Why not?

00:27:33.869 --> 00:27:35.078 line:80%
Listen, Mr. Seong Hyeonguk.

00:27:35.162 --> 00:27:36.913 line:80%
You dare call your father by his name?

00:27:36.997 --> 00:27:38.498 line:80%
You just said you'd disown me.

00:27:39.332 --> 00:27:40.917 line:80%
Then you wouldn't be my dad anyway.

00:27:42.419 --> 00:27:45.297 line:80%
So, Mr. Seong Hyeonguk, to summarize,

00:27:45.380 --> 00:27:46.882 line:80%
I shouldn't bother acting out

00:27:46.965 --> 00:27:49.968 line:80%
because it'll all be
Taeju's in the end, right?

00:27:50.469 --> 00:27:52.220 line:80%
Seong Taeju will be the ultimate winner.

00:27:52.304 --> 00:27:54.347 line:80%
Taeju is so awesome!

00:27:54.848 --> 00:27:56.057 line:80%
That's the gist.

00:27:56.725 --> 00:27:57.726 line:80%
Right?

00:27:58.685 --> 00:28:01.605 line:80%
I should just kill Taeju
and secure my spot in hell.

00:28:01.688 --> 00:28:02.772 line:80%
Seong Huiju!

00:28:02.856 --> 00:28:05.734 line:80%
Anyone who ever tried to pick a fight
with me was exactly like you.

00:28:06.526 --> 00:28:08.945 line:80%
They'd stack the deck
so they couldn't help but win,

00:28:09.029 --> 00:28:11.156 line:80%
and put me in a spot
where I was bound to lose.

00:28:12.908 --> 00:28:14.242 line:80%
I guess they weren't confident

00:28:14.868 --> 00:28:16.328 line:80%
they could win on equal terms.

00:28:19.039 --> 00:28:20.081 line:80%
[sighs deeply]

00:28:20.957 --> 00:28:21.958 line:80%
But you know what?

00:28:22.459 --> 00:28:23.793 line:80%
It's fine.

00:28:24.419 --> 00:28:26.171 line:80%
I'm used to going up against

00:28:27.255 --> 00:28:28.298 line:80%
people like that.

00:28:28.381 --> 00:28:29.799 line:80%
You just won't quit.

00:28:29.883 --> 00:28:30.884 line:80%
I wish you…

00:28:31.760 --> 00:28:32.761 line:80%
all the best.

00:28:34.179 --> 00:28:35.722 line:80%
Though I'm sure you'll lose anyway.

00:29:12.384 --> 00:29:14.553 line:80%
PRINCE

00:29:16.680 --> 00:29:17.847 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:29:25.855 --> 00:29:27.399 line:80%
Sorry for hanging up on you earlier--

00:29:27.482 --> 00:29:28.733 line:80%
[I-AN] <i>Are you okay?</i>

00:29:32.237 --> 00:29:33.405 line:80%
<i>Are you all right?</i>

00:29:36.908 --> 00:29:38.702 line:80%
<i>Seong Huiju, can you not hear me?</i>

00:29:40.745 --> 00:29:42.581 line:80%
Can I call you back tomorrow?

00:29:43.498 --> 00:29:44.499 line:80%
<i>What?</i>

00:29:45.208 --> 00:29:46.543 line:80%
I'm a little busy right now.

00:29:47.877 --> 00:29:48.962 line:80%
I'll call you tomorrow.

00:29:59.431 --> 00:30:00.932 line:80%
[♪ sad music playing]

00:30:04.686 --> 00:30:06.938 line:80%
JUNIOR ALUM

00:30:11.610 --> 00:30:12.736 line:80%
[exhales deeply]

00:30:48.313 --> 00:30:50.815 line:80%
CERTIFICATE OF AWARD

00:30:53.151 --> 00:30:54.402 line:80%
[exhales sharply]

00:31:03.912 --> 00:31:04.913 line:80%
HAPPY BIRTHDAY, TAEJU

00:31:04.996 --> 00:31:06.623 line:80%
HOPE YOU GROW UP
STRONG AND HEALTHY

00:31:08.291 --> 00:31:09.292 line:80%
[sighs]

00:31:13.380 --> 00:31:15.382 line:80%
Buy me a bike too.

00:31:16.383 --> 00:31:18.760 line:80%
The same one as Taeju.

00:31:33.942 --> 00:31:35.402 line:80%
REPORT CARD

00:31:42.117 --> 00:31:43.535 line:80%
I want a building too.

00:31:44.452 --> 00:31:45.829 line:80%
One that's taller than Taeju's.

00:31:53.128 --> 00:31:54.796 line:80%
Amend your will, Father.

00:31:55.380 --> 00:31:56.631 line:80%
In my favor.

00:32:07.559 --> 00:32:08.601 line:80%
[doorbell rings]

00:32:13.690 --> 00:32:14.774 line:80%
Who is it?

00:32:15.442 --> 00:32:16.568 line:80%
[knock on door]

00:32:18.653 --> 00:32:19.988 line:80%
Someone lost their damn mind.

00:32:20.572 --> 00:32:22.115 line:80%
Who the hell is it at this hour…

00:32:25.910 --> 00:32:27.078 line:80%
Damn it.

00:32:30.206 --> 00:32:31.583 line:80%
[♪ dreamy music playing]

00:32:35.879 --> 00:32:41.593 line:80%
♪ <i>Teatime for His Royal Highness!</i> ♪

00:32:42.719 --> 00:32:43.720 line:80%
Your Royal Highness?

00:32:44.429 --> 00:32:46.514 line:80%
Wait, are we playing hide and seek?

00:32:48.516 --> 00:32:49.601 line:80%
What are you doing here?

00:32:49.684 --> 00:32:51.436 line:80%
Wait, are you allowed to be here?

00:32:51.519 --> 00:32:54.022 line:80%
Hold on. Did anyone see you?

00:32:54.105 --> 00:32:55.231 line:80%
Where's Aide Choi?

00:32:55.940 --> 00:32:57.108 line:80%
You play baseball at home?

00:33:01.404 --> 00:33:05.074 line:80%
I have one too many enemies, you see.

00:33:10.455 --> 00:33:11.456 line:80%
Oh.

00:33:11.539 --> 00:33:12.540 line:80%
Wait.

00:33:13.166 --> 00:33:16.002 line:80%
How did you even get here?

00:33:16.085 --> 00:33:17.712 line:80%
Wait, did you come here alone?

00:33:17.796 --> 00:33:18.797 line:80%
[I-AN] Yeah.

00:33:19.923 --> 00:33:21.299 line:80%
[Huiju] You can't just…

00:33:26.679 --> 00:33:27.889 line:80%
Let me get this straight.

00:33:29.015 --> 00:33:30.767 line:80%
You picked these up yourself?

00:33:42.737 --> 00:33:43.822 line:80%
THE SEONG HUIJU COMBO

00:33:43.905 --> 00:33:45.114 line:80%
I will have this one.

00:33:47.075 --> 00:33:48.701 line:80%
Yes, Your Royal Highness.

00:33:49.911 --> 00:33:51.871 line:80%
[I-AN]
<i>"Seduce the Prince" Seong Huiju Combo.</i>

00:33:52.831 --> 00:33:53.832 line:80%
It seemed popular.

00:33:55.667 --> 00:33:57.919 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:33:58.002 --> 00:34:00.213 line:80%
[laughing]

00:34:00.296 --> 00:34:01.506 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:34:05.176 --> 00:34:07.178 line:80%
[♪ regal music plays]

00:34:12.016 --> 00:34:13.101 line:80%
[grunts]

00:34:13.184 --> 00:34:15.144 line:80%
[panting]

00:34:16.521 --> 00:34:17.522 line:80%
Seriously?

00:34:18.022 --> 00:34:21.025 line:80%
[shouting] Couldn't you have left
after you finished your work?

00:34:21.734 --> 00:34:24.237 line:80%
-[grunts]
-[paper rustling]

00:34:24.320 --> 00:34:26.239 line:80%
[humming]

00:34:28.157 --> 00:34:29.158 line:80%
[sighs]

00:34:30.410 --> 00:34:32.370 line:80%
-What is it?
-Just a bit amazed.

00:34:33.162 --> 00:34:34.289 line:80%
By what?

00:34:35.081 --> 00:34:36.624 line:80%
I came because you sounded so down.

00:34:37.417 --> 00:34:40.169 line:80%
But seeing you eat,
you seem perfectly fine.

00:34:41.963 --> 00:34:43.464 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:34:43.548 --> 00:34:44.716 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:34:45.967 --> 00:34:47.093 line:80%
I was a little down.

00:34:47.176 --> 00:34:50.221 line:80%
I was dragged
through the mud all day, you see.

00:34:51.180 --> 00:34:53.766 line:80%
I was barraged
with hate comments on social media.

00:34:53.850 --> 00:34:56.352 line:80%
My father suddenly threatened
to disown me.

00:34:56.436 --> 00:34:57.437 line:80%
Oh, that's right.

00:34:57.937 --> 00:35:01.441 line:80%
I even got egged by your fans today.

00:35:01.524 --> 00:35:04.152 line:80%
I totally forgot to ask
if those eggs were antibiotic-free.

00:35:04.819 --> 00:35:05.987 line:80%
You got "egged"?

00:35:06.070 --> 00:35:07.572 line:80%
Yeah. Two eggs, no less.

00:35:07.655 --> 00:35:10.992 line:80%
Those little pip-squeaks were
so damn strong for no reason.

00:35:12.076 --> 00:35:13.494 line:80%
-It still hurts.
-Here?

00:35:13.578 --> 00:35:15.079 line:80%
Yeah. Just downstairs.

00:35:16.831 --> 00:35:18.416 line:80%
-[Huiju sucks teeth]
-Are you hurt?

00:35:21.920 --> 00:35:22.962 line:80%
Are you hurt anywhere?

00:35:23.922 --> 00:35:25.924 line:80%
[♪ gentle music plays]

00:35:36.309 --> 00:35:39.395 line:80%
[♪ ominous music plays]

00:35:53.326 --> 00:35:55.495 line:80%
[phone chimes, rings]

00:35:58.790 --> 00:36:00.208 line:80%
An investigation is required.

00:36:01.626 --> 00:36:03.628 line:80%
[♪ tense music plays]

00:36:05.421 --> 00:36:06.756 line:80%
They're coming right now?

00:36:06.839 --> 00:36:08.424 line:80%
That's what I said. Now, move it!

00:36:16.349 --> 00:36:18.351 line:80%
She will be staying here
for the time being.

00:36:25.274 --> 00:36:27.777 line:80%
She has been receiving
a troublesome amount of attention.

00:36:28.861 --> 00:36:30.154 line:80%
I was concerned.

00:36:30.905 --> 00:36:32.031 line:80%
So you were…

00:36:33.157 --> 00:36:34.742 line:80%
concerned.

00:36:35.535 --> 00:36:36.619 line:80%
And my instructions?

00:36:36.703 --> 00:36:38.955 line:80%
[stutters]
Everything is ready, Your Royal Highness.

00:36:40.415 --> 00:36:41.791 line:80%
[I-AN clears throat]

00:36:45.837 --> 00:36:46.838 line:80%
Oh!

00:36:47.714 --> 00:36:49.257 line:80%
[♪ upbeat music plays]

00:36:53.970 --> 00:36:55.555 line:80%
Maybe that's a bit too close?

00:37:05.732 --> 00:37:07.984 line:80%
[steward panting]

00:37:10.445 --> 00:37:12.363 line:80%
Please make yourself at home.

00:37:13.823 --> 00:37:16.284 line:80%
What should I call you?

00:37:17.076 --> 00:37:18.661 line:80%
-Pardon?
-How should I address you?

00:37:18.745 --> 00:37:20.580 line:80%
[inhales] Uh…

00:37:22.540 --> 00:37:25.668 line:80%
I am Yeongmun of the Kim Family,
the steward of this residence.

00:37:25.752 --> 00:37:28.629 line:80%
Feel free to call me Steward Kim.

00:37:30.006 --> 00:37:31.883 line:80%
Steward? [chuckles] Hmm.

00:37:32.717 --> 00:37:33.718 line:80%
Yes, ma'am.

00:37:34.427 --> 00:37:35.511 line:80%
[laughing] Steward.

00:37:35.595 --> 00:37:36.763 line:80%
[laughs]

00:37:37.472 --> 00:37:39.390 line:80%
It's late, so I will leave you to rest.

00:37:39.474 --> 00:37:43.144 line:80%
I will give you a proper tour
of the property tomorrow.

00:37:43.227 --> 00:37:44.479 line:80%
All right.

00:37:49.984 --> 00:37:51.110 line:80%
Just a second.

00:37:52.445 --> 00:37:55.990 line:80%
How shall I address you?

00:37:56.616 --> 00:37:57.992 line:80%
Ah. [chuckles]

00:38:02.705 --> 00:38:06.584 line:80%
I prefer Ms. Seong or Executive Director,
but you can call me by my name.

00:38:06.667 --> 00:38:09.170 line:80%
You're not my employee, after all.

00:38:10.338 --> 00:38:11.339 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:38:11.964 --> 00:38:12.965 line:80%
Then, I shall

00:38:13.966 --> 00:38:15.259 line:80%
address you as Your Ladyship.

00:38:16.803 --> 00:38:18.471 line:80%
"Your Ladyship"?

00:38:19.680 --> 00:38:20.848 line:80%
Well then.

00:38:21.390 --> 00:38:22.809 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:38:27.438 --> 00:38:28.648 line:80%
[sighs]

00:38:29.398 --> 00:38:30.525 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:38:31.818 --> 00:38:33.611 line:80%
I was at the palace yesterday,

00:38:33.694 --> 00:38:36.030 line:80%
and today, the prince's private residence.

00:38:36.114 --> 00:38:37.949 line:80%
[phone buzzing]

00:38:41.828 --> 00:38:42.954 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:38:45.373 --> 00:38:46.624 line:80%
Yes, Your Royal Highness.

00:38:47.208 --> 00:38:48.376 line:80%
<i>Do you like your room?</i>

00:38:49.710 --> 00:38:50.711 line:80%
I mean, it's nice.

00:38:51.212 --> 00:38:53.214 line:80%
It feels like I'm on
a historical drama set.

00:38:53.297 --> 00:38:54.340 line:80%
[chuckles softly]

00:38:54.423 --> 00:38:56.092 line:80%
Why aren't you sleeping?

00:38:56.634 --> 00:38:57.760 line:80%
<i>I have some work to do.</i>

00:39:00.763 --> 00:39:02.014 line:80%
Do you want me to help?

00:39:05.601 --> 00:39:07.603 line:80%
[♪ tense music plays]

00:39:20.116 --> 00:39:21.200 line:80%
[door creaks]

00:39:28.332 --> 00:39:29.375 line:80%
[cat meows]

00:39:29.458 --> 00:39:30.877 line:80%
[gasps]

00:39:32.420 --> 00:39:33.713 line:80%
[mews]

00:39:35.506 --> 00:39:37.508 line:80%
[breathes heavily]

00:39:41.345 --> 00:39:42.722 line:80%
[♪ gentle music plays]

00:39:53.858 --> 00:39:55.276 line:80%
[sighs]

00:39:57.111 --> 00:39:59.697 line:80%
So am I really going to live here now?

00:40:01.157 --> 00:40:02.909 line:80%
Well, it's just that

00:40:03.451 --> 00:40:05.870 line:80%
I'm quite an independent woman.

00:40:06.370 --> 00:40:08.206 line:80%
I find this bustling environment…

00:40:09.123 --> 00:40:10.499 line:80%
a bit bothersome, shall I say?

00:40:11.000 --> 00:40:12.543 line:80%
It's so far from work too.

00:40:14.337 --> 00:40:15.922 line:80%
Shouldn't you be more "bothered"

00:40:16.672 --> 00:40:20.092 line:80%
if I were to leave you in harm's way
when I'm supposedly infatuated with you?

00:40:20.176 --> 00:40:21.385 line:80%
Commute aside.

00:40:21.469 --> 00:40:23.095 line:80%
[smacks lips] Okay.

00:40:26.682 --> 00:40:27.975 line:80%
[Huiju sighs]

00:40:29.227 --> 00:40:30.269 line:80%
By the way…

00:40:32.021 --> 00:40:33.314 line:80%
You wanted to help.

00:40:33.397 --> 00:40:34.398 line:80%
Is this you helping?

00:40:35.316 --> 00:40:37.693 line:80%
I don't know anything
about the royal ancestral rites.

00:40:38.194 --> 00:40:40.154 line:80%
I've never even attended
any of my family's.

00:40:46.953 --> 00:40:48.663 line:80%
[sighs]

00:40:48.746 --> 00:40:50.039 line:80%
What do you want to know?

00:40:52.792 --> 00:40:53.960 line:80%
Why are you marrying me?

00:40:54.043 --> 00:40:55.419 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:40:55.503 --> 00:40:57.713 line:80%
Isn't it a bit late to be asking that?

00:40:57.797 --> 00:41:00.299 line:80%
We only made the decision yesterday.

00:41:00.383 --> 00:41:02.593 line:80%
Why can't I be a little curious today?

00:41:04.512 --> 00:41:05.596 line:80%
You have a lot of money.

00:41:06.264 --> 00:41:08.015 line:80%
The richest in the country, no less.

00:41:10.351 --> 00:41:11.811 line:80%
Is that your reason?

00:41:11.894 --> 00:41:13.229 line:80%
The most important reason.

00:41:13.312 --> 00:41:15.898 line:80%
It would help the royal family,
always under fire

00:41:15.982 --> 00:41:17.900 line:80%
for squandering taxpayers' money.

00:41:17.984 --> 00:41:18.985 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:41:19.902 --> 00:41:21.696 line:80%
And what a noble reason it is.

00:41:22.196 --> 00:41:23.698 line:80%
-[sucks teeth]
-Second.

00:41:25.241 --> 00:41:26.617 line:80%
[sighs]

00:41:26.701 --> 00:41:27.743 line:80%
Beauty.

00:41:28.744 --> 00:41:29.787 line:80%
"Beauty"?

00:41:30.371 --> 00:41:33.165 line:80%
Oh, I guess that finally broke through.

00:41:35.209 --> 00:41:36.794 line:80%
-Third.
-What? What now?

00:41:36.877 --> 00:41:38.462 line:80%
Because my family doesn't overstep?

00:41:38.546 --> 00:41:40.589 line:80%
If I say I wish to ascend the throne,

00:41:42.800 --> 00:41:44.927 line:80%
all would condemn me and hurl insults.

00:41:49.265 --> 00:41:50.266 line:80%
But I believe

00:41:51.517 --> 00:41:52.727 line:80%
you would understand me.

00:42:16.792 --> 00:42:19.128 line:20%
The Inner Court Banquet
is still some time away.

00:42:19.211 --> 00:42:21.964 line:20%
Yet I am already being pressed
to make a decision.

00:42:22.048 --> 00:42:24.008 line:20%
It appears they are quite anxious,

00:42:24.091 --> 00:42:26.218 line:80%
as they need to finalize
the guest list soon.

00:42:26.302 --> 00:42:29.889 line:80%
Does Your Majesty have any criteria
in mind for the guest list?

00:42:30.473 --> 00:42:31.599 line:80%
I'm not sure.

00:42:35.019 --> 00:42:38.230 line:80%
Those with exemplary character,
admirable talents,

00:42:39.774 --> 00:42:41.192 line:80%
and innate nobility?

00:42:44.195 --> 00:42:45.905 line:80%
Would that suffice?

00:42:45.988 --> 00:42:47.281 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:42:47.365 --> 00:42:48.240 line:80%
[buzzes]

00:42:56.207 --> 00:42:58.125 line:80%
I must cancel today's itinerary.

00:42:58.959 --> 00:43:00.169 line:80%
Pardon?

00:43:00.252 --> 00:43:01.379 line:80%
But they already--

00:43:01.462 --> 00:43:02.880 line:80%
Surely there should be no issue.

00:43:06.092 --> 00:43:07.802 line:80%
I am indisposed, after all.

00:43:11.847 --> 00:43:14.558 line:80%
[♪ suspenseful music plays]

00:43:19.355 --> 00:43:20.356 line:80%
[exclaims]

00:43:23.192 --> 00:43:25.069 line:80%
[Yeongmun whispering]
Your Ladyship, please wake up.

00:43:30.116 --> 00:43:31.409 line:80%
Your Ladyship, wake up.

00:43:33.077 --> 00:43:34.078 line:80%
Wait, hold on.

00:43:35.830 --> 00:43:38.124 line:80%
How dare you storm in here! Hey, you!

00:43:38.207 --> 00:43:39.291 line:80%
Youngseon!

00:43:39.375 --> 00:43:41.752 line:80%
Why that little prick…

00:43:43.921 --> 00:43:45.089 line:80%
What in the world?

00:43:57.476 --> 00:43:58.477 line:80%
What's this about?

00:43:58.561 --> 00:44:02.273 line:80%
Cooperate with the Junghwajeon Hall
fire investigation, please.

00:44:02.356 --> 00:44:03.774 line:80%
"Cooperate"?

00:44:07.445 --> 00:44:08.821 line:80%
At the Royal Birthday Banquet,

00:44:09.697 --> 00:44:12.450 line:80%
you entered a restricted area
of the palace, didn't you?

00:44:13.576 --> 00:44:15.536 line:80%
I did get lost at one point.

00:44:16.454 --> 00:44:17.455 line:80%
But what about it?

00:44:18.205 --> 00:44:20.583 line:80%
Are you suggesting
I started the fire or something?

00:44:21.167 --> 00:44:22.626 line:80%
Nothing has been ruled out yet.

00:44:22.710 --> 00:44:23.711 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:44:23.794 --> 00:44:27.423 line:80%
You'll need to give a detailed account
of what you did and who you met there.

00:44:28.174 --> 00:44:30.009 line:80%
What exactly am I supposed to explain?

00:44:32.303 --> 00:44:33.846 line:80%
[explosion]

00:44:33.929 --> 00:44:35.473 line:80%
[Huiju] What was that?

00:44:35.556 --> 00:44:36.557 line:80%
You stay here.

00:44:37.308 --> 00:44:39.768 line:80%
You've publicly stated,
"The royal family is a money pit.

00:44:40.269 --> 00:44:43.397 line:80%
Someone should abolish the Crown.
Let's bring out the guillotine."

00:44:43.939 --> 00:44:44.940 line:80%
Is that correct?

00:44:46.650 --> 00:44:47.693 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:44:48.694 --> 00:44:49.695 line:80%
Do you have a warrant?

00:44:49.778 --> 00:44:50.905 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:44:51.989 --> 00:44:54.950 line:80%
Under the Royalty
and Specialist Protection Law,

00:44:55.034 --> 00:44:58.454 line:80%
suspects of royal threats
may be investigated prior to a warrant.

00:44:59.622 --> 00:45:00.664 line:80%
Get started.

00:45:01.624 --> 00:45:03.417 line:80%
Hold on. Take your shoes off.

00:45:04.585 --> 00:45:06.128 line:80%
No, you can't take that!

00:45:12.301 --> 00:45:14.345 line:80%
What do you think you're doing?

00:45:14.428 --> 00:45:16.388 line:80%
-Hold on a second.
-You can't take this!

00:45:16.472 --> 00:45:18.182 line:80%
-[employee 1] What are you doing?
-Move!

00:45:18.265 --> 00:45:20.935 line:80%
-[employee 2] Is this really necessary?
-[agent] Please step aside.

00:45:22.394 --> 00:45:23.604 line:80%
[employee 3] What are you doing?

00:45:23.687 --> 00:45:25.648 line:80%
-This is insane.
-[employee 1] Why are you doing this?

00:45:31.237 --> 00:45:32.613 line:80%
[sighs]

00:45:32.696 --> 00:45:33.864 line:80%
Damn it. What now?

00:45:33.948 --> 00:45:35.658 line:80%
Gosh, you're working so hard.

00:45:35.741 --> 00:45:36.825 line:80%
Have you eaten yet?

00:45:36.909 --> 00:45:38.536 line:80%
-You need to eat something.
-I'm fine.

00:45:38.619 --> 00:45:40.287 line:80%
Let's fill that belly first.

00:45:40.371 --> 00:45:43.916 line:80%
This is His Royal Highness's favorite,
so let's have a taste.

00:45:43.999 --> 00:45:45.376 line:80%
Come on. Take a seat.

00:45:45.459 --> 00:45:48.504 line:80%
Sit down. Let's have a bite while we chat.

00:45:49.004 --> 00:45:50.673 line:80%
Go on. Just try one.

00:45:50.756 --> 00:45:52.299 line:80%
[phone chimes, rings]

00:45:53.717 --> 00:45:56.845 line:80%
Your Ladyship,
you need to eat something too.

00:45:56.929 --> 00:45:58.722 line:80%
Can't be questioned on an empty stomach.

00:45:58.806 --> 00:46:00.599 line:80%
-Go on. It's still warm.
-No thanks.

00:46:00.683 --> 00:46:01.892 line:80%
-Come on!
-Stop it.

00:46:02.476 --> 00:46:04.019 line:80%
I'm calling His Royal Highness.

00:46:05.980 --> 00:46:07.481 line:80%
Why isn't he picking up?

00:46:08.691 --> 00:46:09.942 line:80%
He probably won't answer.

00:46:10.609 --> 00:46:11.610 line:80%
What?

00:46:11.694 --> 00:46:14.113 line:80%
Cell phones are not allowed
during the ritual.

00:46:15.155 --> 00:46:16.156 line:80%
Ritual?

00:46:16.782 --> 00:46:17.866 line:80%
As in ancestral rites?

00:46:39.388 --> 00:46:41.390 line:80%
[Huiju] <i>Ms. Do. You're running, right?</i>

00:46:41.473 --> 00:46:43.309 line:80%
Yes, I'm running.

00:46:43.392 --> 00:46:45.227 line:80%
What a hell of a way to spend the weekend.

00:46:45.311 --> 00:46:47.688 line:80%
What choice do I have?
You're the only one I can trust.

00:46:47.771 --> 00:46:49.106 line:80%
Forget all that.

00:46:49.189 --> 00:46:50.899 line:80%
Prepare to give me a hefty bonus.

00:46:51.483 --> 00:46:52.526 line:80%
Hang up now.

00:46:54.987 --> 00:46:55.988 line:80%
I got this.

00:46:57.865 --> 00:46:59.116 line:80%
She won't get in.

00:46:59.199 --> 00:47:00.576 line:80%
Why not?

00:47:00.659 --> 00:47:01.910 line:80%
She's a civilian.

00:47:02.786 --> 00:47:05.706 line:80%
Civilians may enter Jongmyo Shrine
only on special days.

00:47:06.540 --> 00:47:07.583 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:47:07.666 --> 00:47:08.667 line:80%
Come on.

00:47:10.628 --> 00:47:12.755 line:80%
Oh. Oh!

00:47:12.838 --> 00:47:14.298 line:80%
Huh?

00:47:14.381 --> 00:47:16.550 line:80%
ROYAL PROTECTION BRANCH

00:47:23.057 --> 00:47:24.850 line:80%
[♪ anthemic music plays]

00:47:34.234 --> 00:47:35.235 line:80%
Shall we?

00:47:38.489 --> 00:47:39.740 line:80%
[sighs]

00:47:46.955 --> 00:47:48.248 line:80%
-[agent] Hurry up, ma'am.
-Hold on…

00:47:49.083 --> 00:47:51.001 line:80%
[employee] My goodness.

00:47:51.960 --> 00:47:54.046 line:80%
Wait. I can't believe this.

00:47:54.129 --> 00:47:56.090 line:80%
-Please let me in this once.
-No, you can't.

00:47:56.173 --> 00:47:57.925 line:80%
I'm from Castle Beauty.

00:47:58.008 --> 00:47:59.635 line:80%
I need to see His Royal Highness.

00:47:59.718 --> 00:48:00.803 line:80%
We already told you no.

00:48:01.303 --> 00:48:02.596 line:80%
Just leave already!

00:48:02.680 --> 00:48:04.390 line:80%
How can I when I know he's in there?

00:48:05.265 --> 00:48:07.267 line:80%
[♪ upbeat music plays]

00:48:08.936 --> 00:48:10.479 line:80%
-[Yeongmun] Ms. Do!
-[gasps]

00:48:10.979 --> 00:48:13.607 line:80%
[Yeongmun] Ms. Do!

00:48:14.191 --> 00:48:16.568 line:80%
Ms. Do! Oh, Ms. Do!

00:48:16.652 --> 00:48:18.070 line:80%
Ms. Do…

00:48:21.949 --> 00:48:23.617 line:80%
We come by order of the Grand Prince.

00:48:23.701 --> 00:48:26.453 line:80%
GRAND PRINCE I-AN

00:48:46.056 --> 00:48:47.057 line:80%
Good heavens!

00:48:49.560 --> 00:48:50.644 line:80%
That…

00:48:50.728 --> 00:48:52.604 line:80%
Isn't that the Grand Prince's <i>hopae?</i>

00:48:52.688 --> 00:48:54.690 line:80%
Why was that precious thing in the toilet?

00:48:56.316 --> 00:48:57.901 line:80%
-Steward Kim.
-Yes?

00:49:00.696 --> 00:49:02.072 line:80%
Please take it to Jongmyo.

00:49:03.031 --> 00:49:05.284 line:80%
-Pardon?
-Just in case.

00:49:06.660 --> 00:49:07.703 line:80%
I'm counting on you.

00:49:08.412 --> 00:49:09.413 line:80%
You got this!

00:49:12.666 --> 00:49:13.667 line:80%
Good luck!

00:49:15.043 --> 00:49:16.128 line:80%
Good? Step aside.

00:49:16.211 --> 00:49:18.756 line:80%
I knew it!
You could've just let me pass earlier!

00:49:25.471 --> 00:49:27.222 line:80%
Where are you going? It's this way.

00:49:28.849 --> 00:49:30.726 line:80%
That bonus better be a generous one.

00:49:31.477 --> 00:49:32.519 line:80%
I'm so exhausted.

00:49:37.232 --> 00:49:38.734 line:80%
[drumbeat]

00:50:22.903 --> 00:50:23.904 line:80%
[groans]

00:50:24.488 --> 00:50:26.949 line:80%
Oh, dear. He can't step out
while the ritual is underway.

00:50:27.032 --> 00:50:29.451 line:80%
[Hyejeong panting] It's already started.

00:50:37.918 --> 00:50:38.961 line:80%
Oh.

00:50:40.295 --> 00:50:42.422 line:80%
-If he can't leave…
-Yes?

00:50:42.923 --> 00:50:44.299 line:80%
…we can go in instead.

00:50:45.592 --> 00:50:46.802 line:80%
What?

00:50:59.022 --> 00:51:00.023 line:80%
Huh?

00:51:00.107 --> 00:51:01.859 line:80%
-[whispering] We need to go.
-What?

00:51:01.942 --> 00:51:03.944 line:80%
-We need to go.
-Pardon?

00:51:04.027 --> 00:51:05.028 line:80%
We need to go.

00:51:05.863 --> 00:51:07.781 line:80%
-How did you even get in here?
-Quiet…

00:51:09.783 --> 00:51:11.034 line:80%
We need to go.

00:51:12.452 --> 00:51:13.996 line:80%
We need to go right now.

00:51:18.792 --> 00:51:20.002 line:80%
So…

00:51:21.253 --> 00:51:23.130 line:80%
You're going to question me at the palace?

00:51:30.971 --> 00:51:32.097 line:80%
Seong Huiju!

00:51:32.180 --> 00:51:33.181 line:80%
[gasps]

00:51:40.564 --> 00:51:41.940 line:80%
Mr. Jung.

00:51:42.983 --> 00:51:44.234 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:51:45.611 --> 00:51:48.739 line:80%
I heard the Royal Ancestral Rite
was being held at Jongmyo Shrine today.

00:51:49.323 --> 00:51:51.742 line:80%
-What brings you by?
-His Majesty is presiding over it.

00:51:53.577 --> 00:51:55.329 line:80%
But what business have you here?

00:51:56.705 --> 00:51:59.249 line:80%
Without authorization
from either His Majesty or me.

00:52:02.044 --> 00:52:03.587 line:80%
[Yun] I gave the authorization.

00:52:12.804 --> 00:52:15.933 line:80%
As I heard the prime suspect
in the arson case had been identified.

00:52:16.558 --> 00:52:17.559 line:80%
And since she is…

00:52:19.811 --> 00:52:22.397 line:80%
considered a flight risk
and may destroy evidence.

00:52:24.399 --> 00:52:26.652 line:80%
But I did not know that you would be here.

00:52:28.111 --> 00:52:29.488 line:80%
Is there actually any evidence?

00:52:30.739 --> 00:52:33.200 line:80%
As if insulting the Crown
with such insolent attire

00:52:33.825 --> 00:52:36.536 line:80%
<i>and threatening others</i>
<i>within the palace were not enough,</i>

00:52:37.287 --> 00:52:38.330 line:80%
I hear she was absent

00:52:39.623 --> 00:52:41.291 line:80%
at the time of the incident.

00:52:41.959 --> 00:52:43.585 line:80%
Does that constitute evidence?

00:52:43.669 --> 00:52:44.878 line:80%
[Yun] Perhaps not.

00:52:44.962 --> 00:52:47.547 line:80%
But it should be enough to tarnish…

00:52:49.257 --> 00:52:50.676 line:80%
her reputation

00:52:51.259 --> 00:52:53.095 line:80%
or her company's reputation.

00:52:53.804 --> 00:52:54.972 line:80%
Wait, my company?

00:52:58.558 --> 00:52:59.893 line:80%
Then have me questioned too.

00:53:03.438 --> 00:53:05.941 line:80%
Every circumstance
that casts suspicion on her

00:53:07.109 --> 00:53:08.944 line:80%
applies to me as well.

00:53:18.495 --> 00:53:20.163 line:80%
Will your confidence hold?

00:53:22.249 --> 00:53:23.375 line:80%
I wonder

00:53:25.419 --> 00:53:26.670 line:80%
if yours will hold.

00:53:41.143 --> 00:53:42.853 line:80%
-[screams]
-Ms. Seong!

00:53:46.690 --> 00:53:48.066 line:80%
Oh, Your Royal Highness!

00:53:48.692 --> 00:53:49.943 line:80%
-Summon a physician.
-I-AN.

00:53:50.694 --> 00:53:51.737 line:80%
[grunts]

00:53:51.820 --> 00:53:54.322 line:80%
Feel free to come to Anhwadang Hall
for the questioning.

00:53:57.075 --> 00:53:58.994 line:80%
Summon a physician!

00:53:59.077 --> 00:54:00.328 line:80%
[Hyejeong] Hurry.

00:54:01.955 --> 00:54:03.331 line:80%
[Hyeon] Are you all right, Ms. Seong?

00:54:12.591 --> 00:54:13.842 line:80%
[sighs]

00:54:15.093 --> 00:54:16.303 line:80%
[Huiju grunts]

00:54:28.648 --> 00:54:29.649 line:80%
Open your eyes.

00:54:32.819 --> 00:54:34.613 line:80%
[gasps] Wow.

00:54:35.572 --> 00:54:36.740 line:80%
Wow, we totally slayed!

00:54:36.823 --> 00:54:37.824 line:80%
Slayed, my foot.

00:54:37.908 --> 00:54:39.159 line:80%
[exhales]

00:54:39.242 --> 00:54:40.702 line:80%
How could you agree to come here?

00:54:41.912 --> 00:54:44.706 line:80%
That Mr. Jung or whatever
practically dragged me out.

00:54:44.790 --> 00:54:45.791 line:80%
How could I resist?

00:54:47.334 --> 00:54:48.543 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:54:50.378 --> 00:54:51.379 line:80%
So…

00:54:52.422 --> 00:54:54.049 line:80%
will I be going to prison?

00:54:56.218 --> 00:54:57.219 line:80%
Does that scare you?

00:54:57.302 --> 00:54:58.637 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:54:58.720 --> 00:55:00.013 line:80%
Me?

00:55:00.097 --> 00:55:02.140 line:80%
I'm Seong Huiju of Castle Group.

00:55:02.224 --> 00:55:04.810 line:80%
Prosecutor investigations
and search-and-seizure raids…

00:55:05.310 --> 00:55:06.311 line:80%
Stuff like that

00:55:06.895 --> 00:55:09.523 line:80%
is practically an annual event.

00:55:10.982 --> 00:55:15.320 line:80%
I was just wondering which law firm
I should hire this time.

00:55:15.403 --> 00:55:17.531 line:80%
-Is that something to be proud of?
-[chuckling] I mean,

00:55:18.198 --> 00:55:19.699 line:80%
it's nothing to brag about, but--

00:55:19.783 --> 00:55:21.785 line:80%
She won't be able to act for now.

00:55:21.868 --> 00:55:23.703 line:80%
She knows pursuing you would implicate me,

00:55:24.204 --> 00:55:25.705 line:80%
which would only escalate matters.

00:55:25.789 --> 00:55:26.832 line:80%
[sucks teeth]

00:55:28.959 --> 00:55:30.460 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:55:30.544 --> 00:55:34.005 line:80%
But wouldn't you say
that was quite a display?

00:55:34.589 --> 00:55:35.715 line:80%
What was?

00:55:35.799 --> 00:55:36.925 line:80%
Everyone saw it.

00:55:37.592 --> 00:55:40.762 line:80%
The Queen Mother talked about tarnishing
my reputation or whatever.

00:55:41.263 --> 00:55:42.931 line:80%
And you taking my side.

00:55:43.014 --> 00:55:44.307 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:55:44.391 --> 00:55:45.684 line:80%
[laughs]

00:55:45.767 --> 00:55:47.185 line:80%
Wake up.

00:55:47.269 --> 00:55:49.104 line:80%
Palace staff do not divulge
palace affairs.

00:55:49.604 --> 00:55:51.064 line:80%
[laughs]

00:55:52.232 --> 00:55:53.775 line:80%
Do you really believe that?

00:55:55.443 --> 00:55:58.780 line:80%
They say the mouth is
the gateway to disaster,

00:55:58.864 --> 00:56:01.658 line:80%
and the tongue is
a blade that cuts the body.

00:56:02.159 --> 00:56:04.411 line:80%
Do you know how many mouths were there?

00:56:07.247 --> 00:56:12.043 line:80%
And you think not a single mouth there
has loose lips?

00:56:13.044 --> 00:56:14.254 line:80%
[Huiju chuckles]

00:56:15.213 --> 00:56:19.301 line:80%
They probably whipped up
an entire soap opera out of it by now.

00:56:20.468 --> 00:56:22.220 line:80%
[♪ pop music plays]

00:56:22.304 --> 00:56:23.638 line:80%
[tailor] I can't believe it.

00:56:23.722 --> 00:56:25.640 line:80%
And still in his ceremonial robe?

00:56:26.308 --> 00:56:27.517 line:80%
I mean, it makes sense.

00:56:27.601 --> 00:56:29.561 line:80%
I heard from an attendant
of the Queen Mother…

00:56:29.644 --> 00:56:31.479 line:80%
I thought it was just a passing scandal,

00:56:31.563 --> 00:56:34.399 line:80%
but as soon as she fainted,
he swept her up in his arms.

00:56:34.482 --> 00:56:35.692 line:80%
It caused quite a stir.

00:56:35.775 --> 00:56:37.485 line:80%
It must be true love!

00:56:37.569 --> 00:56:38.820 line:80%
[staff member] I know, right?

00:56:38.904 --> 00:56:40.155 line:80%
[guard] Hmm.

00:56:40.238 --> 00:56:41.948 line:80%
Plenty of people weren't there.

00:56:42.032 --> 00:56:43.992 line:80%
That doesn't make someone a suspect.

00:56:44.075 --> 00:56:46.036 line:80%
She must've been
so shocked that she fainted.

00:56:49.122 --> 00:56:51.458 line:80%
[court lady]
Your Majesty, are you all right?

00:56:51.541 --> 00:56:53.960 line:80%
Please stay there. I will clean this up.

00:56:54.044 --> 00:56:55.128 line:80%
Court Lady Im.

00:56:55.212 --> 00:56:56.421 line:80%
Is anyone out there?

00:56:56.504 --> 00:56:57.714 line:80%
Court Lady Im!

00:57:01.843 --> 00:57:03.637 line:80%
What are your thoughts?

00:57:04.429 --> 00:57:05.472 line:80%
Pardon?

00:57:05.555 --> 00:57:06.806 line:80%
[stammers] About what, Your Majesty?

00:57:08.183 --> 00:57:10.268 line:80%
The Grand Prince and that maiden.

00:57:10.352 --> 00:57:12.062 line:80%
Did they seem

00:57:13.396 --> 00:57:14.898 line:80%
genuine in your eyes as well?

00:57:24.991 --> 00:57:27.035 line:80%
-You're not coming with me?
-I have to work.

00:57:27.118 --> 00:57:28.328 line:80%
But it's the weekend.

00:57:28.870 --> 00:57:29.871 line:80%
If I clock out,

00:57:30.997 --> 00:57:32.123 line:80%
someone will kill me.

00:57:32.207 --> 00:57:33.541 line:80%
Who?

00:57:35.418 --> 00:57:36.795 line:80%
Him.

00:57:38.004 --> 00:57:40.131 line:80%
Oh. [chuckles softly]

00:57:41.132 --> 00:57:42.884 line:80%
Try not to stay up too late, though.

00:57:43.468 --> 00:57:44.552 line:80%
I shall try.

00:57:44.636 --> 00:57:46.721 line:80%
You can call me
if you have trouble sleeping.

00:57:46.805 --> 00:57:48.181 line:80%
[chuckles] I shall.

00:57:59.526 --> 00:58:01.111 line:80%
The more mouths, the better, right?

00:58:24.718 --> 00:58:26.469 line:80%
[♪ upbeat music plays]

00:58:26.553 --> 00:58:27.595 line:80%
[meows]

00:58:49.034 --> 00:58:50.535 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:58:51.870 --> 00:58:52.871 line:80%
[screaming] Your Ladyship!

00:58:52.954 --> 00:58:54.748 line:80%
[Youngseon shrieking]

00:58:56.750 --> 00:58:58.335 line:80%
Are you all right?

00:58:58.418 --> 00:59:00.587 line:80%
What about His Royal Highness?
Is he all right?

00:59:01.880 --> 00:59:02.881 line:80%
Well…

00:59:05.008 --> 00:59:06.968 line:80%
Our dear Steward Kim played a huge role.

00:59:07.052 --> 00:59:09.346 line:80%
I am quite a biker, you see.

00:59:09.429 --> 00:59:10.930 line:80%
Thank you.

00:59:12.182 --> 00:59:13.224 line:80%
Ha!

00:59:13.308 --> 00:59:14.392 line:80%
Applause please.

00:59:14.476 --> 00:59:17.145 line:80%
[cheering]

00:59:17.228 --> 00:59:18.897 line:80%
[Yeongmun] Well done!

00:59:18.980 --> 00:59:19.981 line:80%
[person] <i>All right!</i>

00:59:20.065 --> 00:59:21.107 line:80%
I'm exhausted.

00:59:22.817 --> 00:59:24.235 line:80%
[sighs]

00:59:27.614 --> 00:59:28.615 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:59:33.328 --> 00:59:34.913 line:80%
[laughs]

00:59:35.580 --> 00:59:37.123 line:80%
[phone buzzing]

00:59:40.502 --> 00:59:42.128 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:59:44.631 --> 00:59:45.840 line:80%
Still alive?

00:59:46.466 --> 00:59:48.385 line:80%
-[I-AN] <i>For now.</i>
-[chuckles softly]

00:59:49.844 --> 00:59:52.263 line:80%
I haven't been able to eat,
so I'm starving.

00:59:52.347 --> 00:59:54.808 line:80%
Why not? Is the food not to your liking?

00:59:54.891 --> 00:59:56.434 line:80%
<i>No, I'm just trying to lose weight.</i>

00:59:56.935 --> 00:59:58.061 line:80%
Why?

00:59:58.144 --> 01:00:00.146 line:80%
Looking gaunt will make me
seem more like a victim.

01:00:00.230 --> 01:00:01.398 line:80%
[chuckles]

01:00:02.982 --> 01:00:05.068 line:80%
You'll have the Royal Guard
starting tomorrow.

01:00:05.693 --> 01:00:06.694 line:80%
Really?

01:00:07.195 --> 01:00:09.114 line:80%
Is that allowed
when we're not married yet?

01:00:09.197 --> 01:00:10.407 line:80%
It isn't.

01:00:10.490 --> 01:00:11.533 line:80%
I see.

01:00:12.033 --> 01:00:14.661 line:80%
"Another crazy stunt pulled
by the infatuated Grand Prince"?

01:00:15.495 --> 01:00:17.372 line:80%
I guess you can put it like that.

01:00:17.455 --> 01:00:19.040 line:80%
[laughs]

01:00:21.918 --> 01:00:23.294 line:80%
Should I pull one too?

01:00:29.384 --> 01:00:31.177 line:80%
[♪ gentle music plays]

01:00:39.227 --> 01:00:40.562 line:80%
[car engine starts]

01:01:07.630 --> 01:01:08.840 line:80%
[sighs]

01:01:12.177 --> 01:01:13.678 line:80%
[phone chimes, rings]

01:01:16.723 --> 01:01:18.892 line:80%
[ringtone playing]

01:01:30.695 --> 01:01:31.905 line:80%
[straining]

01:01:35.450 --> 01:01:36.826 line:80%
[laughs]

01:01:38.953 --> 01:01:41.122 line:80%
Never thought I'd be doing this.

01:01:41.206 --> 01:01:43.082 line:80%
[laughs]

01:01:44.834 --> 01:01:50.715 line:80%
[Huiju sighs]

01:01:50.798 --> 01:01:52.509 line:80%
[Huiju straining]

01:01:54.093 --> 01:01:55.678 line:80%
[sighs]

01:01:55.762 --> 01:01:59.599 line:80%
This is the least we can do
to make them think we're madly in love.

01:02:01.017 --> 01:02:02.060 line:80%
Oh, right.

01:02:06.648 --> 01:02:07.649 line:80%
Here.

01:02:08.942 --> 01:02:11.444 line:80%
This is the tea I drink
when I have trouble sleeping.

01:02:12.070 --> 01:02:14.030 line:80%
It's really expensive, so don't waste it.

01:02:15.740 --> 01:02:17.700 line:80%
One more thing…

01:02:20.078 --> 01:02:23.164 line:80%
This is the magnesium supplement
I take when I really can't asleep.

01:02:24.040 --> 01:02:27.669 line:80%
The side effect is nightmares,
but it's better than not sleeping at all.

01:02:30.755 --> 01:02:32.632 line:80%
-When did I ever ask--
-Stop that.

01:02:33.550 --> 01:02:35.969 line:80%
You didn't see a doctor
after what happened, did you?

01:02:38.721 --> 01:02:40.473 line:80%
[scoffs]

01:02:40.557 --> 01:02:43.518 line:80%
Don't you think I'd be
quite the supportive wife?

01:02:45.103 --> 01:02:46.187 line:80%
Hmm.

01:02:48.439 --> 01:02:49.691 line:80%
[chuckles softly]

01:02:50.733 --> 01:02:53.111 line:80%
[♪ gentle music plays]

01:03:07.875 --> 01:03:08.960 line:80%
What are you doing?

01:03:17.552 --> 01:03:18.553 line:80%
Stay still.

01:03:27.145 --> 01:03:29.147 line:80%
[♪ romantic music plays]

01:03:57.967 --> 01:04:00.887 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN

01:04:36.964 --> 01:04:38.758 line:80%
[Huiju] <i>Why would I blush</i>

01:04:38.841 --> 01:04:41.678 line:80%
and get all fluttery over a measly kiss?

01:04:41.761 --> 01:04:44.013 line:80%
[court lady]
<i>You should have maintained decorum.</i>

01:04:44.097 --> 01:04:46.599 line:80%
[I-AN] <i>Then what? Should we make it</i>
<i>a shotgun wedding?</i>

01:04:47.809 --> 01:04:50.687 line:80%
Can I take you somewhere?
Let's speed things up a bit.

01:04:51.270 --> 01:04:53.898 line:80%
<i>The quicker we get married,</i>
<i>the quicker we get divorced.</i>

01:04:54.857 --> 01:04:55.858 line:20%
Smile!

01:04:55.942 --> 01:04:58.695 line:20%
[Huiju] <i>Do you have that much time</i>
<i>to waste?I don't.</i>

01:04:59.320 --> 01:05:02.115 line:20%
[Lord INPYEONG] <i>That maiden</i>
<i>should move out of your private residence.</i>

01:05:02.198 --> 01:05:05.034 line:20%
-[laughs]
-Do you have a plan?

01:05:05.827 --> 01:05:07.120 line:20%
Seong Huiju, what's wrong?

01:05:07.203 --> 01:05:09.997 line:20%
Jeongwoo! The brakes aren't working!

01:05:10.081 --> 01:05:11.791 line:20%
[horn honking]

01:05:15.837 --> 01:05:18.131 line:20%
Why aren't you answering?

01:05:18.798 --> 01:05:21.092 line:20%
Will you take their side and not mine

01:05:21.175 --> 01:05:23.136 line:20%
because they're your family?

01:05:23.219 --> 01:05:24.178 line:80%
[scoffs]

01:05:25.430 --> 01:05:26.639 line:80%
[scoffs]

01:05:28.057 --> 01:05:29.225 line:20%
I will take your side.

01:05:38.067 --> 01:05:39.152 line:20%
I must appear

01:05:40.111 --> 01:05:41.654 line:20%
insanely infatuated with you…

01:05:46.033 --> 01:05:47.827 line:20%
[♪ acoustic pop song plays]

01:05:50.663 --> 01:05:52.039 line:20%
…for people to believe

01:05:53.958 --> 01:05:55.543 line:20%
this absurd marriage is genuine.

01:06:12.643 --> 01:06:14.645 line:20%
-What's that?
-It's my <i>hopae</i>.

01:06:15.646 --> 01:06:16.647 line:20%
What about it?

01:06:18.065 --> 01:06:20.109 line:20%
Use it when you need a title behind you

01:06:20.193 --> 01:06:21.319 line:20%
or when you are afraid.

01:06:23.654 --> 01:06:26.616 line:20%
Does it summon a dragon
if I swing it around or something?

01:06:34.582 --> 01:06:35.583 line:20%
It'll summon me.

01:06:46.844 --> 01:06:48.846 line:20%
Translated by Justin S. Kim

01:07:00.149 --> 01:07:03.861 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN